452
00:35:33,320 --> 00:35:35,197
Just get in the car.

453
00:35:37,120 --> 00:35:38,872
Hombres, vamonos.

454
00:35:58,320 --> 00:36:00,151
- (baby crying)
- What's the matter?

455
00:36:00,280 --> 00:36:02,874
Please don't cry. Shh, it's OK.

456
00:36:03,080 --> 00:36:05,674
- Shh.
- (crying continues)

457
00:36:05,800 --> 00:36:08,553
- What did you do to her?
- I didn't do anything to her.

458
00:36:08,680 --> 00:36:10,671
You must have done something.

459
00:36:10,800 --> 00:36:14,349
Chloe, look, I promise you,
I didn't do anything to her.

460
00:36:14,480 --> 00:36:18,519
I'm gonna redirect all my files back
down to my desk. I'm finished with this.

461
00:36:18,640 --> 00:36:22,713
Jack and Nina are meeting Amador
in 53 minutes in a place called Posta Mita.

462
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:26,230
- What about Delta Force?
- They've established a perimeter of 3km.

463
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:28,880
- (baby screaming)
- What the hell is that?

464
00:36:28,880 --> 00:36:30,871
Dammit. I told her.

465
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:35,397
Michelle, you take care of this, please.

466
00:36:37,640 --> 00:36:41,394
- That's it, Chloe. You're out of here.
- I said I didn't have anyone to watch her.

467
00:36:41,520 --> 00:36:44,159
You'll watch her.
I gave you a warning. You're suspended.

468
00:36:44,240 --> 00:36:47,198
- It was a verbal warning only.
- Ryan.

469
00:36:50,160 --> 00:36:53,391
- What?
- Jack's meeting Amador in less than an hour.

470
00:36:53,520 --> 00:36:55,829
We have no visual satellite coverage
of that area.

471
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:58,189
What does that have to do with this baby?

472
00:36:58,360 --> 00:37:02,399
We have to use digitally enhanced audio
coverage. Chloe is the best we have at that.

473
00:37:02,480 --> 00:37:05,870
You're telling me we have to let
this woman raise her child in our office

474
00:37:06,160 --> 00:37:07,832
because no one can do her job?

475
00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:11,759
Maybe we should deal with
Chloe's childcare problems on another day.

476
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:15,715
OK, thatta girl.

477
00:37:17,880 --> 00:37:18,915
(cries)

478
00:37:19,240 --> 00:37:22,869
I have work to do.
Who's gonna look after my child?

479
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:27,599
- Give her to Kim.
- What?

480
00:37:27,880 --> 00:37:30,872
Based on what CTU got from Jack,
the meeting will take place here,

481
00:37:31,200 --> 00:37:32,872
by an old mine north of town.

482
00:37:33,200 --> 00:37:34,952
My position is gonna be here.

483
00:37:35,320 --> 00:37:38,880
I need you to put your men behind this ridge
until we know that the virus is real.

484
00:37:38,880 --> 00:37:41,519
Good natural cover. That'll work.

485
00:37:41,640 --> 00:37:45,633
- How long will it take your men to get there?
- 90 seconds.

486
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:47,876
- Thank you.
- Good luck.

487
00:38:28,680 --> 00:38:31,513
- Where are the rest of the men?
- Felipe brought everyone.

488
00:38:31,640 --> 00:38:34,791
- There's not enough.
- Amador is only bringing one man.

489
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:36,313
So he says.

490
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:39,352
- Stop making problems.
- I'm making sure we are covered.

491
00:38:39,480 --> 00:38:41,880
You want to stop this
because you lost your nerve.

492
00:38:41,880 --> 00:38:45,031
Things are moving fast.
We haven't had time to think them through.

493
00:38:45,320 --> 00:38:47,880
- We'll be fine.
- That doesn't mean we'll be fine.

494
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:50,792
The situation is difficult enough.
Don't make it worse.

495
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:55,708
Or what?

496
00:38:55,840 --> 00:38:58,752
Ram Ãn, if you want this deal to happen,
we have to leave now.

497
00:38:58,880 --> 00:39:00,880
We have to be there
20 minutes before Amador.

498
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:03,474
The deal is off!

499
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:16,871
All right.

500
00:39:26,560 --> 00:39:29,880
- Hector, we're not done here.
- I've said what I need to say.

501
00:39:29,880 --> 00:39:32,110
Listen to me, Hector.
Listen to me carefully.

502
00:39:32,440 --> 00:39:34,715
If we don't give our buyers
what you promised,

503
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:37,877
we won't just lose money, we'll lose respect.

504
00:39:38,600 --> 00:39:40,830
And without that, we have nothing.

505
00:39:44,880 --> 00:39:46,871
We'll have our lives.

506
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:51,076
We're leaving now.

507
00:39:52,640 --> 00:39:53,868
Pablo, Felipe, vamonos.

508
00:39:58,880 --> 00:40:00,711
Now!

509
00:40:06,040 --> 00:40:08,998
Hector, don't do this.

510
00:40:21,120 --> 00:40:23,076
Hector!

511
00:40:24,880 --> 00:40:26,836
Hector!

512
00:40:27,480 --> 00:40:29,436
Hector!

